      <name>gregorw</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/12545</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;In&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/cp-cf-create-destination.html#1fe610de-dede-4fc2-b41e-29bd9079ba06" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Step 4 Create a new destination&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;I can see that the destination is created manually. So it seems that the Instance destination in your mta.yaml was added by one of the yeoman generator steps. Have you tracked the steps with git commits? So you could find out. I would suggest that you remove everything starting at&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;config. Maybe&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/898"&gt;@nicoschoenteich&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;can have a look here and do adjustments to the tutorial.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/application-development-discussions/can-t-create-destination-service-for-a-ui5-app-for-build-work-zone/m-p/13855967#M2030822"/>
